Class EdgeList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vividsolutions.jts.geomgraph.EdgeList

  • public class EdgeList
extends java.lang.Object
    A EdgeList is a list of Edges. It supports locating edges that are pointwise equals to a target edge.
